            <note xml:id="foot.f8">See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 4, letters to J. D. Hooker, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-1085.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">[1 May 1847]</ref>, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-1086.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">[6 May 1847]</ref>, and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-1087.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">[12 May 1847]</ref>. CD referred to this incident in his <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_261.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Autobiography</hi></ref>, p. 105.</note>
